HEADWORD: Lactucone
<hw>Lac*tu"cone</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<er>Lactuca</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A white, crystalline,
tasteless substance, found in the milky sap of species of Lactuca, and
constituting an essential ingredient of lactucarium.</def>⟦br⟧
